prototype.commodities.dataaccess
Class Month

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--prototype.commodities.dataaccess.Month
public class Month
extends java.lang.Object

The Month class is a table lookup of the variety of representations that are used for a given month in the commodities market.

Author:
J.R. Titko
